window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A marriage of convenience. A dangerous betrayal. A trust neither expected to build.</p> <p>Alex Stone is no stranger to high stakes, but when his carefully constructed world teeters on the brink of collapse, the one person he turns to is the wife who’s ready to walk away. Ava agreed to help him uncover a dangerous conspiracy targeting his company—but she didn’t expect to find herself in the crosshairs.</p> <p>As threats escalate and their marriage of convenience is tested, Alex and Ava must navigate a web of secrets, betrayal, and simmering emotions. With their bond deepening under the pressure, Alex faces his most personal battle yet: convincing Ava that their partnership is more than a business arrangement—it’s a chance at real love.</p> <p>When trust is the only thing standing between survival and destruction, Alex and Ava must decide if they’re willing to risk their hearts to save each other. But will the dangers they face tear them apart before they can find their happily ever after?</p> <p>If you love forced proximity, high-stakes drama, and a dash of intrigue, you’ll be captivated by <i>Stone’s Throw to Trust</i>—a gripping second installment in Alex and Ava’s unforgettable journey.</p> <p>Listen now and fall in love today!</p>"; 
